works.description:
The Aston Martin One-77 is an extremely  
special edition supercar limited to only 77 units worldwide. While a
One-77  
was sold lately for a whopping $7.21 million in China, a businessman from 

Christchurch in New Zealand has spent a cool $2.8 million to get behind
the  
wheels of this exotic car. At $2.8 million, the Aston Martin One-77  
supercar is being said to be the most expensive car ever ordered by a Kiwi
 
buyer.
